# E-State — Design Tokens Rules

Backed by [docs/design-system.md](mdc:docs/design-system.md) and [docs/design-brief.md](mdc:docs/design-brief.md).

## Colour palette (only source of truth: Tailwind config)

Canonical tokens in `apps/web/tailwind.config.ts`:

- `forest` (`#3F5E3B`) — primary actions
- `olive` (`#B6B774`) — secondary accents
- `sand` (`#E3C9A9`) — background blocks
- `rose` (`#C97A7F`) — alerts / critical
- `surface`, `ink`, semantic `success | warning | info | danger`

**No raw hex in JSX, CSS, or inline styles.** Use Tailwind classes against the declared tokens. New colours must be added to the Tailwind config and to [docs/design-system.md](mdc:docs/design-system.md) in the same commit.

## Components

- Use Shadcn primitives only (`Button`, `Badge`, `Table`, `Dialog`, `DropdownMenu`, `Select`, `Input`, `Label`, `Textarea`, `Tabs`, `Sheet`, `Toast`, `Skeleton`). Install via `npx shadcn@latest add …`.
- Icons from `lucide-react` only. Stroke width 1.75. Sizes: 20 px in tables, 24 px in hero sections.
- Prohibited libraries: `antd`, `@mui/*`, `react-select`, `chakra-ui`, `semantic-ui`.

## Radius and shadows

- Radius: `rounded-lg` (8 px) dense UI, `rounded-xl` (12 px) hero cards and dialogs. No raw `border-radius`.
- One depth token only: `shadow-soft`. Nothing harder.

## Status badges

Every status must render with **label + icon + tone** — never colour alone. Mapping table lives in [docs/design-system.md §6](mdc:docs/design-system.md#6-status-badges). Missing or ad-hoc mappings are not allowed.

## Typography

- Inter variable via `next/font`. Mono for tax IDs and cadastral numbers.
- Tabular numerals (`font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums`) on tables and metric cards.

## Accessibility

- Every interactive element is keyboard-reachable with a visible focus ring (`focus-visible:ring-2 ring-forest/60`).
- Body text never smaller than 16 px; `text-sm` only for labels / captions.
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.
- Status never communicated by colour alone.

## Anti-template policy

Follows [.cursor/rules/web-design-quality.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/web-design-quality.mdc). Additionally banned for E-State:

- Default Shadcn theme without palette swap.
- Generic centred-gradient hero on any non-marketing page.
- Rainbow severity badges.
- Uniform 16 px padding rhythm.
